= About

I am now a research assistant at the department of BioMedical Engineering (BME), [http://www.fmmu.edu.cn FMMU], co-work with *Prof. Xiuzhen Dong* and *Prof. Feng Fu*. I am also a fifth-year Ph.D at the Science and Technology on Automatic Target Recognition Laboratory (ATR Lab), [http://www.nudt.edu.cn NUDT], under the supervisor of *Prof. Qiang Fu* and *Dr. Hongqi Fan* in Adavance Radar Signal Processing *(ARSP)* group. My research interests lie broadly on biomedical signal processing, statistics, optimization, tracking and estimation.

